What:           /sys/kernel/debug/habanalabs/hl<n>/command_submission_jobs
Date:           Jan 2019
KernelVersion:  5.1
Contact:        oded.gabbay@gmail.com
Description:    Displays a list with detailed information about each JOB (CB) of
