What:           /sys/kernel/debug/habanalabs/hl<n>/stop_on_err
Date:           Mar 2020
KernelVersion:  5.6
Contact:        oded.gabbay@gmail.com
Description:    Sets the stop-on_error option for the device engines. Value of
                "0" is for disable, otherwise enable.
